src:
PICS: Prince Harry meets the Springboks (and a half-naked Faf) in locker room after Rugby World Cup win!

02 Nov 2019, 19:36




































Prince Harry meets the Springbok squad in Japan after their victory against England in the Rugby World Cup 2019 final. (Photos: Handout/World Rugby via Getty Images)
